# Phase 5 Working Files vs Final Output
# =====================================
# DO commit:    lego_baskets.json (final merged output)
# DON'T commit: phase5_outputs/* (working files - too large)
#
# Workflow:
# 1. Generate phase5_outputs/seed_*.json (stays local)
# 2. Run: node scripts/merge_phase5_to_lego_baskets.cjs
# 3. Commit only lego_baskets.json to git

# Course Data - Pipeline State Preservation
# ==========================================
# KEEP phase outputs (pipeline state):
# - Phase 1: seed_pairs.json (~500KB stripped of metadata)
# - Phase 3: lego_pairs.json (~2MB stripped of metadata)
# - Phase 5: lego_baskets.json (~5MB, final merged output with all LEGO baskets)
# - Phase 6: introductions.json (~500KB, presentation content)
#
# IGNORE intermediate/working files:
public/vfs/courses/*/phase5_outputs/         # Individual seed baskets (merged into lego_baskets.json)
public/vfs/courses/*/phase5_scaffolds/        # Phase 5 input scaffolds (derivable)
public/vfs/courses/*/*.cjs                    # Scripts
public/vfs/courses/*/gate_*.json              # Reports
public/vfs/courses/*/grammar_*.json           # Reports
public/vfs/courses/*/infinitive_*.json        # Reports
public/vfs/courses/*/*_report.json            # Reports
public/vfs/courses/*/*_changelog.json         # Reports
public/vfs/courses/*/*_errors.json            # Error logs
public/vfs/courses/archive/                   # Old versions

